## Navigation Architecture

```
App Launch
  └─> Splash Screen
        └─> Onboarding Carousel (first-time users)
              └─> Auth Flow
                    ├─> Sign Up (Email or Google)
                    │     └─> Phone OTP Verification
                    │           └─> Profile Confirmation (Settings)
                    │                 └─> Home Dashboard
                    ├─> Sign In
                    │     └─> Home Dashboard
                    └─> Forgot Password
                          └─> Select OTP Method (Email/Phone)
                                └─> Enter OTP
                                      └─> Set New Password
                                            └─> Login

Home Dashboard (with Bottom Nav)
  ├─> Tab 1: Home (default) — Move Request Form + Status Cards
  ├─> Tab 2: TBD
  ├─> Tab 3: TBD
  └─> Tab 4: TBD

Move Card Tap → Move Details Screen
```

